<%= render partial: "shared/mailers/header", formats: [:html], locals: { title: "Your MAT Application Account" } %>

<h1>Your MAT Application Account</h1>

<p>Dear <%= @constituent.first_name %>,</p>

<p>An administrator has created an account for you in our system based on your paper application submission.</p>

<p>You can now access your application online using the following credentials:</p>

<div style="background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 16px; margin: 16px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
  <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @constituent.email %></p>
  <p><strong>Temporary Password:</strong> <%= @temp_password %></p>
</div>

<p>For security reasons, you will be required to change your password when you first log in.</p>

<p>
  <a href="<%= @login_url %>" data-no-track style="display: inline-block; background-color: #4f46e5; color: white; padding: 8px 16px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;">
    Sign in here
  </a>
</p>

<p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team.</p>

<%= render partial: "shared/mailers/footer", formats: [:html], locals: { show_automated_message: true } %>
